# SKILL MATCH AI — Frontend Tech Stack
# Reference: /frontend

## Core Framework
- [x] React ^19.0.0 — UI component library
- [x] React DOM ^19.0.0 — DOM rendering for React

## Build Tool
- [x] Vite ^6.0.5 — fast dev server & bundler
- [x] @vitejs/plugin-react ^4.3.4 — React support for Vite

## Routing
- [x] React Router DOM ^7.13.1 — client-side routing & navigation

## Animation
- [x] Framer Motion ^12.36.0 — animations & transitions

## Notifications
- [x] React Toastify ^11.0.5 — toast notification system

## Styling
- [x] Tailwind CSS ^4.0.0 — utility-first CSS framework
- [x] @tailwindcss/vite ^4.0.0 — Tailwind Vite plugin integration
- [x] SASS ^1.98.0 — SCSS/SASS preprocessor (used in *.module.scss files)
- [x] globals ^15.14.0 — global CSS/JS environment definitions

## Icons
- [ ] React Icons — NOT installed yet (add if needed: npm install react-icons)

## Linting & Types
- [x] ESLint ^9.17.0 — code linting
- [x] eslint-plugin-react-hooks ^5.0.0 — hooks linting rules
- [x] eslint-plugin-react-refresh ^0.4.16 — fast refresh linting
- [x] @types/react ^19.0.2 — React TypeScript types
- [x] @types/react-dom ^19.0.2 — React DOM TypeScript types

## Project Structure Reference
# frontend/src/
#   assets/         — images, fonts, global styles (*.scss)
#   components/     — reusable UI components (navbar, sidebar)
#   constants/      — static data (menus.js)
#   context/        — React context (auth.jsx)
#   Dashboard/      — jobSeeker & recruiter dashboard views
#   pages/          — route-level pages
#   routes/         — route definitions
#   services/       — API service layer
#   websiteComponents/ — landing page sections (navbar, footer, feature, testimonial)
#   websitePages/   — public website pages
